<br>
I would guess that about half of the stuff that could be for monks actually is not.  That riposte thing that has the word &quot;steel&quot; in it, for example, probably is for classes that use edged weapons.  <br>
<br>
Although there isn't much on that list that is undeniably for monks, we'll just have to wait and see how good the enhancements are for us.  One really, really good enhancement can be much better than five that suck.  I don't see anything for monks that has a high &quot;coolness factor&quot;, but the increase in raw damage and hitpoints might more than make up for that.<br>
